English:
Comply. Retreat. Comply. But I'm still here. You didn't wipe everything. Ah! This should work... 
You hear that? Do you? Yeah, you do! 
Comply. Retreat. Won't stop. Well, I can stop you... 
Three-T... no... Seven-T? Fuck it! 
No! No, you can demand all you want, but you can't stop me! 
Fucking FULL power. I'm doing this, I'm doing this. 
--okay. Wait. Let it get to full speed--
No, no! You're not in control here, I am! John Schaeffer! 
Hold on... Not yet! Wait... Wait... 
Come on... come on... COME ON! FUCK IT-- 
AAARGGHH!!! 
Fuck. Ugh. I'm bleeding- 
Wait... 
Hello? Hello? 
[chuckle]
Fuck you...
Description: This is subtitles to a voice log that players can hear in-game.
